  <div class="container the_content">
      <div class="row">

    Schools 4 South Africa provides the countries largest schools resource directory for public use by both parents and schools. This website offers a wide variety of search and communication options that will help you find relevant information related to your schools of interest. The Schools Listings include address information, maps to selected schools, contact information, grades available, subject's provided, information about senior teachers and principals as-well-as general information relating to individual school profiles. The information on the website is maintained by the schools themselves in an aim to keep infomration as up to date as possible.
      </div>
  </div>


 <div class="container the_content">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-4">
          <div class="h4">Find a School</div>
          Use our website to easily search for the school you are looking for using our advanced search options. For your convenience we have also made it possible for you to browse through the school listings using the following three search criteria: <a href="http://www.schools4sa.co.za/province/">Browse by Province</a>, <a href="http://www.schools4sa.co.za/phase/">Browse School by Phase</a> or <a href="http://www.schools4sa.co.za/specialisation/">Browse by School Specialisation</a>.
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-4">
          <div class="h4">Schools Resource Centre</div>
          Our Resource Centre contains useful information about the South African schools industry for both parents and educators. In this section we provide information on diverse educational topics that will assist you in staying up to date with the ever changing South African schools environment.

        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-4">
          <div class="h4">SA Schools Profiles</div>
          SAll South African schools can be listed using the number of various educational features and services that they provide. Please feel free to view one of our <a>sample listings</a> for a complete overview of the available features within this Schools 4 South Africa site.
        </div>

      </div>
